						               													<description>In an alternative near future, Badass Force is the name of the most famous live show of the ultra-net.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each week, contestants compete to find out who is the most Badass of all!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the arena, it&amp;rsquo;s a no-holds-barred fight, where contestants use technology to take the appearance and abilities of &amp;quot;historical&amp;quot; characters. But alas, our culture is now limited to the action movies of the end of 20th century / early 21st century and many of those recordings have deteriorated.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This week you have finally been selected: Guns, attitude and bluffing will be necessary to fulfill your destiny!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Badass Force, the goal is to be the first to achieve 16 victory points on the badassometer. Points are earned by eliminating the opposing characters, but a player is NEVER ELIMINATED from the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the beginning of the game, seven different characters are selected from the ten in the box. Each player retrieves a copy of each of these seven characters and a weapon card. Players then choose a character from their hand and put it face down in front of them. In turn, a player will increase the level of charge of their weapon AND choose an action from five options (changing characters / changing weapons / fetching ammunition by throwing the 2 weapons dice / using their weapon / announcing a Character to use their power): everyone plays in turn order until a winner is declared.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Badass Force is a thematic game, with strong interaction in which one must use bluffing, guessing, hand management, and a little tactics to succeed and being declared the most Badass of all!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
